"content": "<p>A large plant growing in marshland, sometimes to a height of six metres.</p>\n<h2>Papyrus was used for making boats</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:3\">EXO 2:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:26\">JOB 9:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa18:2\">ISA 18:2</a></p>\n<h2>Papyrus indicates an ample water supply</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:11-Job8:13\">JOB 8:11–8:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:7\">ISA 35:7</a> <em>Papyrus growing in what was once desert depicts the blessing coming on God's redeemed people.</em></p>",
